title: "Gbg-INST-TreeSeg"
abstract: >-
  Tree-crown instance segmentation pipeline for large aerial orthophoto mosaics,
  combining an AerialFormer semantic prior with Cellpose-SAM flow-guided instance
  separation. Independent implementation of the method described in FG-TreeSeg
  (Chen et al., 2026).
type: software
authors:
